      <section eId="sec_354">
        <num>354</num>
        <heading>Restrictions on assignments of compensation for services</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_354__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the assignment by its terms is revocable at the will of the\nborrower; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_354__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the assignment is a payroll deduction plan.\n  2. No assignment of wages or other earnings given to secure any loan\nhereunder shall be valid unless the amount of such loan is paid to the\nborrower simultaneously with its execution.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
